snippet.title: Best VGM 1367 - The Magical Land of Wozz - Vehicle Battle
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
The Magical Land of Wozz (1995)
Vehicle Battle
Tomoyuki Hamada, Takeshi Sato & Seiichi Tokunaga
